<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13981</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19604</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在宽广的海底，有一个世界叫海底王国。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19605</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这个王国在大海深处，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26677</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是连锚都不能到达的海底深处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32245</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>深到陆地上的人们也不可能到访。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在海底王国，到处都是蓝色的海水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37042</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41812</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里的水像海面的波浪一样起伏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47020</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当大海很平静时，阳光照到这个深处。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47021</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55679</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在安静的夜晚，月亮和星星发出的白光会在水中闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55680</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海底生长着最美丽的树。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64506</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的树有紫色的树枝和绿色的叶子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64507</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那里还有五颜六色的花园。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>植物都随着波浪慢慢地摇摆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81651</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>各种大大小小的鱼在叶子和花儿之间游来游去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81652</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它们整天玩儿，睡在岩石之间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人鱼们住在海底王国里，他们有男的也有女的。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人鱼们喜欢跟鱼朋友们一起玩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96970</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101800</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>美人鱼也喜欢用她们美丽的双手喂鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101801</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108125</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>像鱼儿朋友们一样，人鱼们也有尾巴帮他们游泳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112560</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人鱼们爱大海和里面的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112561</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116341</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们从来没想过去别的地方生活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116342</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121473</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们能活很长时间，大概三百年。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121474</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128522</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人鱼们在花园里唱歌、玩儿，幸福地度过每一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135151</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很久以前，一个国王住在大海最深处的一座王宫里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135152</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139676</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他和他的六个女儿生活在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139677</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的王宫有亮橙色的珊瑚墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑色的贝壳覆盖着屋顶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黑色贝壳随着潮水的变化开合。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152033</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贝壳打开时，里面都会有一颗发光的银色珍珠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163345</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>海底国王很善良，统治着水底的所有生物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163346</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他希望大家都幸福。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他过得很伤心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好伤心，我的妻子——王后，很多年前去世了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182938</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他叹了口气，“现在，我一个人照顾六个女儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182939</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>190875</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不，你不是一个人。”他的妈妈——智慧人鱼说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>190876</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192904</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我也在照顾她们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192905</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198357</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>还有我让这个王宫保持整洁、干净。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿子，你总是忘记我在这里做的一切！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204264</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您说的对，妈妈。”海底国王笑着说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213322</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这个家幸亏有您。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213323</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216868</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>智慧人鱼对整个世界很了解。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220078</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把她的孙女们教得很好。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220079</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>224795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等你们准备好了，”她总是这样告诉公主们，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>224796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230814</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会告诉你们关于地上世界的生活。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230815</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>姐妹们各差一岁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234871</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当每个公主满十五岁时，她就可以游到海面上去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241292</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那时，那个公主就第一次看到地上世界。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247236</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>公主们觉得海底王国的生活简单、幸福。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252419</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>256815</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她们每天都很开心，笑声不断。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>256816</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259863</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可是，最小的妹妹不一样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259864</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264563</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很安静、爱思考、有点独特。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264564</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268624</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为她是年纪最小、身材最小的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268625</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都叫她小美人鱼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>